					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Do any games (or modern demos) for NES explicitly (ab)use the PAL-specified scanline chroma blending? I mean the bit where PAL's chroma goes through a [0.5 0.5 0] vertical filter.<br /><br />There are definitely examples of games for consoles that had a more vibrant career in PAL-land, such as Mayhem in Monsterland for the C64.</div>

